reviews.title: Very good breakfast!
reviews.text: Nice breakfast, good coffee and interesting items on the menu. We found that the barista breakfast could use some „modularity“ since one of us would have liked more savory than sweet options.

reviews.title: Fresh sandwiches in a peaceful setting
reviews.text: It's a quiet place that offers fresh products. The sandwiches are amazing. The staff is friendly. The room is peaceful and bright. This is the perfect place to take a break and relax.

reviews.title: Best coffee!
reviews.text: Best coffee in town! Good cookies and cakes, and very nice staff. I would absolutely recommend to visit this place.

articleContent.title: Why Greenville, SC is the perfect mix of adventure and luxury

seoInfo.metaDescription: There are few places that blend luxury and outdoor adventure like Greenville, South Carolina. The days (and mild weather) are made for adrenaline rushes of all types, while the region’s spas, fine dining, and boutique properties serve up luxury experiences that last well into the evening. It’s not hard to dive into a handful of the many treats on offer, and crafting an itinerary that incorporates a little bit of everything is how you’ll find yourself with a Greenville-shaped spot forever in your heart.
